<item>
            <title>[LU-1625] Test failure on test suite parallel-scale-nfsv4, subtest test_metabench</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1625</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4a115426-cba8-11e1-8847-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4a115426-cba8-11e1-8847-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_metabench failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test failed to respond and timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the log, this test took more than 35 minutes before it was ended. I check several pass runs, it usual takes less than 1800s, so the test may just be killed by the system. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
